!-----THIS IS COMMON/INCLUDE FILE DPCOZ3.INC-----
!     THIS IS THE PRIMARY COMMON FOR DIMENSION REDUCTION VIA SCRATCH AREA
!
!     ORIGINAL--AUGUST      2007.
!
!  MOST OF THE REAL SCRATCH STORAGE IS IN DPCOZZ.INC AND
!  DPCOZ2.INC.  HOWEVER, THE MAIN ROUTINE STILL CONTAINED AN
!  ADDITIONAL 5 VARIABLES THAT WERE PASSED TO MAINGR AND MAINAN.
!  I RECODED MAINGR TO NOT USE THESE ARRAYS (I.E., ALL ARRAYS
!  ARE DIMENSIONED IN THE LOW LEVEL GRAPHICS ROUTINES).  HOWEVER,
!  MAINAN STILL USES 4 OF THESE ARRAYS.  AS A SHORT-TERM FIX,
!  DPCOZ3 WILL ACCOMODATE THESE 4 ARRAYS.  IN THE LONG RUN, I
!  PLAN TO MOVE THE STORAGE TO THE LOWER LEVEL ANALYSIS ROUTINES.
!
!
      PARAMETER (KGARB1=1)
      PARAMETER (KGARB2=MAXOBV+1)
      PARAMETER (KGARB3=2*MAXOBV+1)
      PARAMETER (KGARB4=3*MAXOBV+1)
      PARAMETER (KGARB5=4*MAXOBV+1)
      PARAMETER (KGARB6=5*MAXOBV+1)
!
      REAL G3RBAG
      COMMON/RGARB3/G3RBAG(KGARB0)
!
